  "text": "Each participant was required to complete the abovementioned instrument which was not developed by the researcher. This was an open questionnaire which was developed by Zeithmal, Parasuraman & Berry [CITATION_1] to also obtain demographic information including gender, number of years the client had been using the health facility, etc. The questionnaire was a five dimension one which spoke to how satisfaction and expectation were is measured.",
